{"pageid":101311,"pagename":"2017 Midsummer event","title":"2017 Midsummer event","displaytitle":"2017 Midsummer event","revid":14031618,"redirects":["Midsummer event 2017","Midsummer 2017","2017 midsummer event"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"2017_Midsummer_event.png"},{"name":"description","value":"The 2017 Midsummer event was an event that started on 30 June 2017 that lasted for two weeks. Players had to assist Hotpheex in Taverley, helping him protect nature from evil corrupting spirits."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox no-parenthesis-style infobox-event\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"infobox-header\" colspan=\"5\">2017 Midsummer event\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-image infobox-full-width-content\" colspan=\"5\"><a href=\"/w/File:2017_Midsummer_event.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"2017 Midsummer event.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/2017_Midsummer_event.png/300px-2017_Midsummer_event.png?c3a60\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2017_Midsummer_event.png/450px-2017_Midsummer_event.png?c3a60 1.5x, /images/thumb/2017_Midsummer_event.png/600px-2017_Midsummer_event.png?c3a60 2x\" data-file-width=\"1280\" data-file-height=\"874\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Released\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/29_June\" title=\"29 June\">29 June</a> <a href=\"/w/2017\" title=\"2017\">2017</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Midsummer_2017\" title=\"Update:Midsummer 2017\">Update</a>)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">End date\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/20_July\" title=\"20 July\">20 July</a> <a href=\"/w/2017\" title=\"2017\">2017</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:F2P_Castle_Wars\" title=\"Update:F2P Castle Wars\">Update</a>)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Event_rewards\" title=\"Event rewards\">Reward</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Hand_fan\" title=\"Hand fan\">Hand fan</a>, <a href=\"/w/Hornwood_helm\" title=\"Hornwood helm\">Hornwood helm</a>, <a href=\"/w/Mask_of_balance\" title=\"Mask of balance\">Mask of balance</a>, <a href=\"/w/Druidic_wreath\" title=\"Druidic wreath\">Druidic wreath</a>, <a href=\"/w/Disk_of_returning\" title=\"Disk of returning\">Disk of returning</a>, <a href=\"/w/Half_full_wine_jug\" title=\"Half full wine jug\">Half full wine jug</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Preceded by\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/2016_Midsummer_event\" title=\"2016 Midsummer event\">2016 Midsummer event</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Succeeded by\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">N/A\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>2017 Midsummer event</b> was an event that started on 30 June 2017 that lasted for two weeks. Players had to assist <a href=\"/w/Hotpheex\" title=\"Hotpheex\">Hotpheex</a> in <a href=\"/w/Taverley\" title=\"Taverley\">Taverley</a>, helping him protect nature from evil corrupting spirits.\n</p>\n<table id=\"toctemplate\" align=\"left\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"clear:left; margin-bottom:0.5em; margin-right:1em; float:left; padding:0.5em 1.4em 0.8em 0; background:none; width:auto;\" class=\"nomobile\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Walkthrough\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Walkthrough</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Riddles\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Riddles</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Rewards\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Rewards</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"clear-template clear-both\" style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Walkthrough\">Walkthrough</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/2017_Midsummer_event?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/2017_Midsummer_event?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Speak to <a href=\"/w/Hotpheex\" title=\"Hotpheex\">Hotpheex</a> in the druidic circle in <a href=\"/w/Taverley\" title=\"Taverley\">Taverley</a>. He will be attempting to perform the annual summer ritual to <a href=\"/w/Guthix\" title=\"Guthix\">Guthix</a> as a thanks for creating <a href=\"/w/Gielinor\" title=\"Gielinor\">Gielinor</a>, as well as keeping it in balance, as Guthix requested.\n</p><p>However, the druids are missing something, so Hotpheex will refer you to a dwarf, <a href=\"/w/Thordur\" title=\"Thordur\">Thordur</a>, who is familiar with the ritual. Because he cannot leave the altar, you must visit him on his behalf. He will give you a <a href=\"/w/Disk_of_returning\" title=\"Disk of returning\">disk of returning</a>, and teleport you to the <a href=\"/w/Dwarven_Mine\" title=\"Dwarven Mine\">Dwarven Mines</a>. Use the <i>Activate</i> option on the disk, NOT the <i>Blackout</i> option.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:Thordur_facepalm.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/Thordur_facepalm.png/300px-Thordur_facepalm.png?33f1e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"256\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Thordur_facepalm.png/450px-Thordur_facepalm.png?33f1e 1.5x, /images/thumb/Thordur_facepalm.png/600px-Thordur_facepalm.png?33f1e 2x\" data-file-width=\"927\" data-file-height=\"791\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:Thordur_facepalm.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Thordur facepalms.</div></div></div>\n<table class=\"musicplayer\" style=\"clear:left; float:left;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Faint_noise.ogg\" title=\"File:Faint noise.ogg\"><img alt=\"Audio options icon.png\" src=\"/images/Audio_options_icon.png?84afb\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a></div><b>Faint noise</b>\n<div style=\"margin-left:0px;\">The faint noise that can be heard when the riddle appears in the player's chatbox.</div>\n<div class=\"mediaContainer\" style=\"width:300px\"><audio id=\"mwe_player_0\" controls=\"\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width:300px\" class=\"kskin\" data-durationhint=\"2.2465306122449\" data-startoffset=\"0\" data-mwtitle=\"Faint_noise.ogg\" data-mwprovider=\"local\"><source src=\"/images/Faint_noise.ogg?4d3ed\" type=\"audio/ogg; codecs=&quot;vorbis&quot;\" data-title=\"Original Ogg file (56 kbps)\" data-shorttitle=\"Ogg source\" data-width=\"0\" data-height=\"0\" data-bandwidth=\"55730\" /><source src=\"/images/transcoded/Faint_noise.ogg/Faint_noise.ogg.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\" data-title=\"MP3\" data-shorttitle=\"MP3\" data-transcodekey=\"mp3\" data-width=\"0\" data-height=\"0\" data-bandwidth=\"105376\" /></audio></div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Once you are in the <a href=\"/w/Blackhole\" title=\"Blackhole\">blackhole</a>, speak to Thordur, who will be frustrated because there was no offering given during the ritual, and that this occurs every year. He asks you to listen to the faint noise, and that it is the riddle to tell the player what is necessary for the ritual to work. Use the <i>Activate</i> option on the disk of returning to leave the blackhole, you will find yourself in the Dwarven Mines of Falador.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:2017_Midsummer_event_ritual.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2017_Midsummer_event_ritual.png/250px-2017_Midsummer_event_ritual.png?196e4\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"250\" height=\"179\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2017_Midsummer_event_ritual.png/375px-2017_Midsummer_event_ritual.png?196e4 1.5x, /images/thumb/2017_Midsummer_event_ritual.png/500px-2017_Midsummer_event_ritual.png?196e4 2x\" data-file-width=\"830\" data-file-height=\"595\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:2017_Midsummer_event_ritual.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A player performing the ritual.</div></div></div>\n<p>Make your way back to Hotpheex with the answer to the riddle in your inventory, and use the item on the altar. Hotpheex will thank you for your efforts and give you a <a href=\"/w/Half_full_wine_jug\" title=\"Half full wine jug\">Half full wine jug</a>, and that players should repeat the ritual tomorrow, and that doing so three times will earn a special reward.\n</p><p>After each day, players will have to solve a new riddle by speaking to Hotpheex again, and having him teleport you to Thordur again. Doing so will get another half full wine jug and another disk of returning each day. Players who repeat the ritual three times will receive a <a href=\"/w/Hand_fan\" title=\"Hand fan\">hand fan</a> (and for those players who do not already have them, a <a href=\"/w/Hornwood_helm\" title=\"Hornwood helm\">hornwood helm</a>, <a href=\"/w/Mask_of_balance\" title=\"Mask of balance\">mask of balance</a> and <a href=\"/w/Druidic_wreath\" title=\"Druidic wreath\">druidic wreath</a>).\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Riddles\">Riddles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/2017_Midsummer_event?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Riddles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/2017_Midsummer_event?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Riddles\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th>Riddle\n</th>\n<th>Answer\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14 July\n</td>\n<td>A famous pirate missing his voice has a semi-precious stone.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Black_bead\" title=\"Black bead\">Black bead</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13 July\n</td>\n<td>Bellow to find the right note we hear fish\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Raw_tuna\" title=\"Raw tuna\">Raw tuna</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12 July\n</td>\n<td>This tree can blow over and be chopped up.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Willow_logs\" title=\"Willow logs\">Willow logs</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11 July\n</td>\n<td>I would drink this, but it sounds like it would taste unpleasant\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Vial_of_water\" title=\"Vial of water\">Vial of water</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10 July\n</td>\n<td>Undermining we hear flames in a circle we can recoil.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Sapphire_ring\" title=\"Sapphire ring\">Sapphire ring</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9 July\n</td>\n<td>We hear it is part of a part to eat.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Incomplete_pizza\" title=\"Incomplete pizza\">Incomplete pizza</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8 July\n</td>\n<td>Pwned with a little maul.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Hammer\" title=\"Hammer\">Hammer</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7 July\n</td>\n<td>Search for a backward door missing a hole and find some sardines.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Fishing_rod\" title=\"Fishing rod\">Fishing rod</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6 July\n</td>\n<td>Shout in pain before death to recolour.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Yellow_dye\" title=\"Yellow dye\">Yellow dye</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5 July\n</td>\n<td>Imprisoned for holding water.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Jug\" title=\"Jug\">Jug</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4 July\n</td>\n<td>One in midday about to make you cry.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Onion\" title=\"Onion\">Onion</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3 July\n</td>\n<td>Money! Money! So you can eat.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Bread_dough\" title=\"Bread dough\">Bread dough</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2 July\n</td>\n<td>Eating the post we hear while wearing this.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Goblin_mail\" title=\"Goblin mail\">Goblin mail</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1 July\n</td>\n<td>Pale pipe about a dessert.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Apple_pie\" title=\"Apple pie\">Apple pie</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>30 June\n</td>\n<td>Wearing the real about granite super poisoned love.\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Leather_gloves\" title=\"Leather gloves\">Leather gloves</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rewards\">Rewards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/2017_Midsummer_event?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/2017_Midsummer_event?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Disk_of_returning\" title=\"Disk of returning\">Disk of returning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Half_full_wine_jug\" title=\"Half full wine jug\">Half full wine jug</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Druidic_wreath\" title=\"Druidic wreath\">Druidic wreath</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Mask_of_balance\" title=\"Mask of balance\">Mask of balance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Hornwood_helm\" title=\"Hornwood helm\">Hornwood helm</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Hand_fan\" title=\"Hand fan\">Hand fan</a></li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Events\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Events\" title=\"Template:Events\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Events\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Events?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Holiday_events\" title=\"Holiday events\">Holiday and community events</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\"><img alt=\"Box of chocolate strawberries.png\" src=\"/images/Box_of_chocolate_strawberries.png?3d026\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"31\" height=\"26\" data-file-width=\"31\" data-file-height=\"26\" /> Valentine's Day</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/2014_Valentine%27s_Day_event\" title=\"2014 Valentine&#39;s Day event\">2014</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\"><img alt=\"Prop sword.png\" src=\"/images/Prop_sword.png?e5f4c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"26\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"26\" /> Birthday</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/2014_Birthday_event\" title=\"2014 Birthday event\">2014</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/2015_Birthday_event\" title=\"2015 Birthday event\">2015</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/2016_Birthday_event\" 